videos.description: Lagerald Vick gives Kansas a 6-5 lead with an uncontested dunk.
videos.headline: Vick unguarded on dunk to give Kansas early lead

videos.description: Kansas continues to dominate in the paint, with David McCormack making the Jayhawks' 4th dunk of the first half.
videos.headline: McCormack hangs on rim after dunk
